evaluation.response:
It can be really tough to feel like you're not connected to others in that one area anymore. It's sometimes helpful to acknowledge those feelings as they arise.

It's okay to let go of things that are bringing you pain.

It can be much more fun to talk online than being face to face.&#x20;

Even though things don't feel like they're changing right now, that doesn't mean they won't ever. Even when things seem like they're going to stay the same forever, be open minded and see what turns up.&#x20;
